6... Nxe4 7. d3 Ng3 8. Bxf4 Qe7+ 9. Be2 { Greed will be punished: } 9... Nxh1
10. Bg5 Qb4+ 11. c3 Qxb2 12. Nf6+
{ With a completely winning position. If Black goes  12...Kd8  then  13.Nd5+  seals the deal. }
