10... Qe7 11. Qe2 { 11.O-O ?  Nxd5!  12.exd5  Qe3+-+ } 11... Re8 12. O-O-O
{ Black probably needs to agree to a slightly worse endgame now. } 12... Na6
13. Rhe1 Nb4
{ If  13...c4  then  14.Nxc4  Nb4  15.e5±  and White is crushing through. } 14.
a3 { We don't need to worship this bishop too much. } 14... Nxd3+ 15. Qxd3
{ Now e4-e5 is inevitable. } *

