8. O-O g6 9. Ne1 Bg7 10. d5 Ne5 11. Bxh5 gxh5 12. Bxf4 Bg4 13. Qc1
{ White trades away active pieces and starts collecting weak pawns. We avoid Qd2 to stay away from Nc4 ideas. }
