16. Qf2 Nhxf3 17. Nxf3 Bxe5 18. Nxe5 Rxe5 19. Rxd4 Qg5+ 20. Kb1 Be6 21. h6
{ The dust has settled, but not really. White still has massive attacking possibilities! }
