10... c6 11. Bc4 { 11.e5  d5  12.Bd3  Nxe3  13.Qxe3  Be6  and Black is solid. }
11... Nd7 12. Bb3 Qe7 13. Rde1 Nxe3 14. Rxe3 Nb6 15. a4 a5
{ After a5 has been played, Black never wants to castle queenside. } 16. Ree1
O-O 17. Nd1
{ With such a dominant center, White will have time for all necessary maneuvers. }
