9. Nxa7+ Kb8 10. Nb5 { White is likely the favorite in a pawn race. } 10... g5
11. O-O c6 12. Nc3 g4 13. Ne1
{ It's not so easy for Black to open our king since it's defended by our rook and knight. }
13... e5 14. a4 Qg6 15. a5
{ The e4-pawn is of course weak, but we don't care and play for an attack. White has the initiative. }
