Nxe4 { 6...d6  transposes to 5...d6 6.Nxg4 Nf6. } 7. d3 Ng3 8. Bxf4
{ Our main idea. } 8... Qe7+ 9. Be2 Rg8 10. Bxg3 Rxg4 11. Bf2 Rxg2
{ This would be very pleasant for White if there was no exchange sacrifice. }
12. Nc3 d5 13. Qd2 Rxf2 14. Kxf2 Be6 15. Bf3 Nc6
{ Another good-looking draw ahead. } 16. Nxd5 Qc5+ 17. d4 Nxd4 18. Nf6+ Ke7 19.
Ng8+ Ke8 20. Nf6+
{ If Black goes for  20...Kd8  then  21.c3  will be winning. } *

