7... dxc4 { It is quite remarkable that this move isn't that bad. } 8. Bxc4
{ 8.gxh5  g4!  is actually better for Black, as we can't properly hold on to the extra piece. }
8... Ng7
{ Not a pretty square for the knight, but potentially it is not forced to stay there and may jump to e6 in the future. }
